			axios(

					process.env.REACT_APP_DARKSKYKEY
				}/${lat},${lng}`,
				{ method: 'GET', mode: 'no-cors' }
			).then(
				response => {
					const data = response.data;
					setData({ data }, () => {
						resolve();
					});
				},
				error => {
					props.onError('darksky', error);
					reject();
				}
			);
		});
	}
